---
title: Cross-Domain Handshake
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Orch as Spec Orchestrator
    participant Simula as Simula Pack
    participant Reg as Regulations Pack
    participant TB as Trial Balance Pack
    participant PDF as PDF Build & Validation

    Orch->>Simula: publish registry v1.2 (manifest frozen)
    Simula-->>Orch: artefact - schema-registry v1.2
    Orch->>Reg: consume registry v1.2 (taxonomy IDs)
    Reg-->>Orch: artefact - governance obligations
    Orch->>TB: consume registry + obligations
    TB-->>Orch: artefact - tb-corpus v1.2
    Orch->>PDF: build spec PDFs
    PDF-->>Orch: validation pass - spec PDFs published
